## One known issue (logged in ISSUES.md)

`CLICKHOUSE_URL` carries the HTTP port (8123), but `./clickhouse client` connects via native TCP (port 9000). The script passes the URL port as `--port`, so running `pnpm migrate` against a default local ClickHouse will need `CLICKHOUSE_URL=http://localhost:9000` to reach the native TCP port. This is an integration concern outside the unit-test scope.
