## Key finding: runtime bug (not a sprint contract failure)

`runMigration()` passes `--port=8123` (HTTP port) to `./clickhouse client`, which speaks the native TCP protocol on port 9000. `pnpm migrate` will fail by default against a local ClickHouse. The bug is documented in `ISSUES.md`. Score is 8 rather than 9 because the primary deliverable doesn't work out of the box — a follow-up sprint should fix the port handling.
